pageProduct.name: Optimum Nutrition Pure Pro 35 Chocolate 355ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Heavy On Protein Stingy With Fat & Sugar Packed with 35g of high quality protein and only 1g of fat and sugar, Pure Pro 35 is teeming with naturally occurring Essential Amino Acids & BCAA’s to maximise your recovery and help you realise greater goals. Why Use Pure Pro 35? • 35g of Protein per Serving • Great Taste • Naturally Occurring Essential Amino Acids & BCAA’s • Only 1g of Fat & Sugar What Is Pure Pro 35 Used For? • Supporting Lean Muscle Growth & Maintenance • Repairing & Rebuilding Muscle • Supporting Muscle Recovery • Convenient On-The-Go High Protein Shake

Warnings

To be consumed as part of a balanced & nutritious diet, not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women. Should only be used under medical or dietetic supervision.

Common Uses

Muscle recovery, post exercise, anytime protein convenience

Ingredients

Water, Protein Blend 11.5% (Milk Protein Concentrate, Calcium Caseinate [MILK], Whey Protein Concentrate [MILK]), Cocoa Powder (1.3%), Natural Flavours, Stabilisers (Sodium phosphate-dibasic, Gellan Gum, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Sodium Carboxymethylcellulose), Sweetener (Sucralose), Salt

Directions

How To Use Pure Pro 35 This convenient on-the-go high protein shake is ready to work before and after training, in between meals, or any other time that you need to maximise your muscle recovery.
